    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute stunner. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014I\u2019ve totally babied this car since day one! There\u2019s not a mark on it, and the interior is just pristine. It drives like an absolute dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for that perfect ride that feels brand new, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
